networkviewer
Class VisualRule

java.lang.Object
  networkviewer.VisualRule

public class VisualRule
extends java.lang.Object

Holds information in the form of prefuse visual objects about a rule. After the visualization has launched, this also acts as a holder for the bubbleset aggregateItems. Before the bubbles are viewed, the pack method must be called.

Author:
ams292
